WEBVTT

00:01.401 --> 00:03.635
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da,
ba-da-ba-da-ba ♪

00:03.670 --> 00:05.137
♪ Da, da, da-ba-da, da, da ♪
Let's go!

00:05.172 --> 00:06.838
♪ We'll be there ♪

00:06.873 --> 00:09.508
♪ A wink and a smile
and a great old time ♪

00:09.543 --> 00:11.710
♪ Yeah, we'll be there ♪

00:11.745 --> 00:13.812
♪ Wherever we are,
there's some fun to be found ♪

00:13.847 --> 00:16.148
♪ We'll be there
when you turn that corner ♪

00:16.183 --> 00:17.482
♪ We'll jump out the bush ♪

00:17.517 --> 00:19.184
♪ With a big bear hug
and a smile ♪

00:19.219 --> 00:20.619
♪ We'll be there ♪

00:27.682 --> 00:29.382
Panda: Hmm.

00:29.417 --> 00:30.884
Whoa! Anime Con!

00:30.919 --> 00:32.185
Hey, this is today.

00:32.220 --> 00:33.453
Do you want to go
check this out?

00:33.488 --> 00:34.487
[ Slurping ]

00:34.522 --> 00:35.822
Uh, yeah, sure,

00:35.857 --> 00:37.357
when I'm, uh, less busy.

00:37.392 --> 00:38.858
[ Slurping continues ]

00:38.893 --> 00:40.326
Dude, you're not
doing anything.

00:40.361 --> 00:43.363
Uh, I'm drinking
this royal milk tea.

00:43.398 --> 00:45.331
Hey,<i> you</i> want
to go with me?

00:45.366 --> 00:47.166
Ice Bear would rather
check out meat convention.

00:47.201 --> 00:50.136
Meat convention?! Oh, I'm down
for that! Meat rules.

00:50.171 --> 00:53.473
Dude, I'm a vegetarian,
and I thought<i> you</i> were busy.

00:53.508 --> 00:54.574
[ Sighs ]

00:54.609 --> 00:56.175
Okay, I lied.
I'm not busy.

00:56.210 --> 00:58.378
It's just that...
anime's not our thing.

00:58.413 --> 01:00.680
Ice Bear only watches
meat-related anime.

01:00.715 --> 01:02.248
Dude, what are
you staring at?

01:02.283 --> 01:03.650
Huh? What?

01:03.685 --> 01:05.885
...and one medium peach milk tea
with boba comes to $10.52.

01:05.920 --> 01:07.086
Were you staring
at that girl?

01:07.121 --> 01:09.022
Ice Bear saw a smile.
- What? No!

01:09.057 --> 01:10.323
You should totally
talk to her, man.

01:10.358 --> 01:13.359
Mm-- I mean,
Sh-- should I? But how?

01:13.394 --> 01:15.028
Brother, just watch.
Talk about meat.

01:15.063 --> 01:16.729
Wait!
W-what are you doing?

01:16.764 --> 01:18.698
Oh, hi.
Can I help you?

01:18.733 --> 01:20.066
Yes, you can!

01:20.101 --> 01:21.935
My brother Panda,
[giggles] he likes you!

01:21.970 --> 01:23.236
He's, like,
super nice!

01:23.271 --> 01:25.004
Ice Bear thinks
he's a solid six.

01:25.039 --> 01:26.539
No! What the heck
are you saying?

01:26.574 --> 01:28.241
Check him out -- He's sitting
right over there.

01:28.276 --> 01:29.842
That handsome guy,
stuff around his eyes.

01:29.877 --> 01:31.077
[ Groaning ]

01:31.112 --> 01:34.113
Huh? Hey, Pan Pan!
Where you going?

01:34.148 --> 01:36.616
[ Computer beeping ]
Nope, nope,

01:36.651 --> 01:38.551
nope, nope.

01:38.586 --> 01:39.852
Oh, "My Sassy Heart!"

01:39.887 --> 01:41.387
Let's watch this!
I heard it was amazing!

01:41.422 --> 01:43.289
Eh, let's just watch
"Hot Dog Ninja" again.

01:43.324 --> 01:45.725
What? Come on! We watched that,
like, eight times already!

01:45.760 --> 01:47.393
[ Laughs ] Yeah, man.
It's that good.

01:47.428 --> 01:49.262
Come on, I've been
wanting to watch this, dude.

01:49.297 --> 01:51.564
Okay, well, let's
just put it to a vote.

01:51.599 --> 01:53.733
Who wants to watch
"My Little Poopy Heart"?

01:53.768 --> 01:55.301
It's called
"My Sassy Heart"!

01:55.336 --> 01:58.237
Or how about
"Hot Dog Ninja"?

01:58.272 --> 02:00.073
Ugh!
You guys always win!

02:00.108 --> 02:02.942
"Hot Dog Ninja"
doesn't even make any sense.

02:02.977 --> 02:06.012
[ Speaking in Korean ]

02:12.820 --> 02:14.487
[ Cellphone chimes ]
Hey, what the --

02:14.522 --> 02:16.556
Buddy Maker?

02:16.591 --> 02:17.957
Hmm.

02:17.992 --> 02:20.893
"Meet new compatible friends."

02:20.928 --> 02:22.729
That sounds pretty cool.

02:22.764 --> 02:24.597
Step one -- upload a photo.

02:24.632 --> 02:25.598
Okay.

02:25.633 --> 02:26.966
[ Camera shutter clicks ]

02:27.001 --> 02:29.802
Next, um, survey...

02:29.837 --> 02:31.104
Favorite color? Red.

02:31.139 --> 02:33.773
Favorite shape?
Hmm. Circle.

02:33.808 --> 02:34.941
Movie? [ Chuckles ]

02:34.976 --> 02:36.509
Romance of course.

02:36.544 --> 02:37.944
[ Jingle plays ]

02:37.979 --> 02:39.746
Hmm, Tom.

02:39.781 --> 02:42.315
Computerized voice:<i> Would you</i>
<i>like to schedule a hangout?</i>

02:42.350 --> 02:43.950
Uh, sure.

02:43.985 --> 02:45.785
<i>Schedule confirmed.</i>

02:45.820 --> 02:47.787
[ Sighs ]

02:47.822 --> 02:50.957
Hmm...Tom.

02:55.163 --> 02:56.963
[ Cellphone chimes ]

03:00.802 --> 03:04.103
Uh, excuse me,
a-are you Panda?

03:04.138 --> 03:06.472
Huh? Uh, yeah -- yeah.
That's me.

03:06.507 --> 03:08.341
I'm Tom. May I sit?

03:08.376 --> 03:10.943
Uh, yeah! Of course.
Sit, please.

03:10.978 --> 03:12.979
Thanks.
It's nice to meet you.

03:13.014 --> 03:14.714
[ Giggles ]
Likewise.

03:14.749 --> 03:16.816
Heh. This is
a bit awkward.

03:16.851 --> 03:18.618
[ Laughs nervously ]
Yeah, sorry.

03:18.653 --> 03:20.319
I've -- I've never
done this before.

03:20.354 --> 03:21.354
Me neither.

03:21.389 --> 03:23.523
So, uh, what made you
try Buddy Maker?

03:23.558 --> 03:25.558
I just clicked on an ad.
I don't know.

03:25.593 --> 03:27.894
I just wanted to find
someone like, um...

03:27.929 --> 03:28.961
Like you?

03:28.996 --> 03:30.530
Uh, yeah, exactly!

03:30.565 --> 03:32.231
[ Laughs ] Cool.

03:32.266 --> 03:35.301
So, I saw you're into
Korean dramas?

03:35.336 --> 03:37.136
Yeah, I got into this
show called "My Sass" --

03:37.171 --> 03:38.504
"My Sassy Heart"!

03:38.539 --> 03:39.806
I love that show!

03:39.841 --> 03:40.840
[ Gasps ]
Really?!

03:40.875 --> 03:42.575
Hey, you're back!

03:42.610 --> 03:44.010
Uh...
- It's me.

03:44.045 --> 03:45.878
You came in with your
brothers the other day.

03:45.913 --> 03:48.147
You wanted my number,
remember?

03:48.182 --> 03:50.016
Oh, I --
I-I -- I'd --

03:50.051 --> 03:51.417
I'd like
the tofu salad, please.

03:51.452 --> 03:54.520
Oh, okay.
One tofu salad.

03:54.555 --> 03:56.422
So, Panda,
do you want my...?

03:56.457 --> 03:58.057
Um, are you
a vegetarian?

03:58.092 --> 03:59.559
Uh-huh.
Wait, are you?

03:59.594 --> 04:01.661
Yeah, and allergic to
any kind of nuts!

04:01.696 --> 04:04.063
[ Gasps ] I'm also a victim
of nut allergies!

04:04.098 --> 04:05.598
Really?
I don't believe it!

04:05.633 --> 04:07.600
Nobody knows the kind
of suffering we go through.

04:07.635 --> 04:10.103
I know! I was gonna get
the tofu salad, too!

04:10.138 --> 04:11.704
Dude, we should just
share one!

04:11.739 --> 04:13.039
Uh, yeah! Okay!

04:13.074 --> 04:15.041
So, Panda,
do you want my number?

04:15.076 --> 04:16.876
Meh, just the salad,
please.

04:16.911 --> 04:18.111
Okay.

04:18.146 --> 04:19.512
One salad.

04:19.547 --> 04:21.581
And please make sure
there's no nuts in it!

04:21.616 --> 04:22.949
Thank you!

04:22.984 --> 04:24.383
Man,
she's really pretty.

04:24.418 --> 04:26.219
Anyway,
where were we?

04:26.254 --> 04:28.254
I don't know,
- but we have a lot in common.

04:28.289 --> 04:29.622
I'm just so glad
I met you.

04:29.657 --> 04:31.023
[ Laughs ]

04:31.058 --> 04:32.391
Me too.

04:32.426 --> 04:35.628
♪♪

04:35.663 --> 04:38.098
[ Camera shutter clicks ]

04:45.106 --> 04:46.639
[ Giggling ]

04:46.908 --> 04:48.608
[ Giggling ]

04:49.677 --> 04:50.977
[ Giggling continues ]

04:51.012 --> 04:52.278
Grizz: Dude!
Where have you been?

04:52.313 --> 04:53.713
We've been waiting for,
like, an hour!

04:53.748 --> 04:54.747
Ice Bear is starving.

04:54.782 --> 04:56.215
Oh, shoot!
I totally forgot!

04:56.250 --> 04:58.084
We were supposed to get pizza!
I'm sorry, man.

04:58.119 --> 04:59.752
I was having too much fun
with Tom.

04:59.787 --> 05:01.120
Tom, these are my brothers.

05:01.155 --> 05:03.422
-Oh, hey what's up? I'm Grizz.
-Ice Bear.

05:03.457 --> 05:05.091
Oh, hey, you guys
are kind of matching.

05:05.126 --> 05:06.259
You're like twins!
[ Laughs ]

05:06.294 --> 05:08.461
I know, right?
Tom's so awesome.

05:08.496 --> 05:09.996
We have
so much in common!

05:10.031 --> 05:11.564
I love anime.

05:11.599 --> 05:12.965
And I love anime!

05:13.000 --> 05:14.133
I'm vegetarian.

05:14.168 --> 05:16.235
And I'm vegetarian, too!

05:16.270 --> 05:17.770
[ Both giggle ]

05:17.805 --> 05:19.939
Okay. Are we
ready for pizza?

05:19.974 --> 05:21.274
Oh, can Tom join us?

05:21.309 --> 05:23.075
It's okay, I don't
want to impose.

05:23.110 --> 05:24.744
It's cool, man.
Right?

05:24.779 --> 05:25.978
Uh...

05:26.013 --> 05:27.180
sure.

05:27.215 --> 05:28.948
I'll race you
to the bus stop!

05:28.983 --> 05:30.249
Hey, wait for me!

05:30.284 --> 05:31.818
[ Both laughing ]

05:31.853 --> 05:34.620
[ Italian music playing ]

05:34.655 --> 05:36.589
Mmm! Oh, this looks
delicious!

05:36.624 --> 05:38.457
Thank you!
All right, dig in!

05:38.492 --> 05:41.627
Oh, actually, that slice
was touching a meat slice.

05:41.662 --> 05:42.662
I can't eat it.

05:42.697 --> 05:43.596
What?

05:43.631 --> 05:45.031
Just give him
a better slice, man.

05:45.066 --> 05:46.599
Okay, okay.
Thanks, Griff.

05:46.634 --> 05:49.001
It's Grizz.
[ Clears throat ]

05:49.036 --> 05:51.337
So, uh, we went to check out
the meat convention, and --

05:51.372 --> 05:53.139
So, what did you think
of last night's episode?

05:53.174 --> 05:56.142
Holy cow! Do you think Kisuk's
will finally tell her the truth?

05:56.177 --> 05:57.877
He has to!
- It's almost the season finale!

05:57.912 --> 05:59.178
This is getting creepy.

05:59.213 --> 06:00.680
Ice Bear getting
heebie-jeebies.

06:00.715 --> 06:02.882
Maybe tomorrow you can come over
to my place and watch it!

06:02.917 --> 06:04.150
Yeah!

06:04.185 --> 06:05.818
Oh, wait, that would end
pretty late, though.

06:05.853 --> 06:06.853
How would I get back?

06:06.888 --> 06:08.221
You could just
stay over.

06:08.256 --> 06:10.323
That way we can talk about
the show all night long!

06:10.358 --> 06:12.358
Or maybe re-watch
the entire show!

06:12.393 --> 06:15.027
[ Laughs ]
Nothing can stop us!

06:15.062 --> 06:17.063
[ Giggling ]
Check, please.

06:17.098 --> 06:18.831
All right, dude.
I'll see you tomorrow.

06:18.866 --> 06:20.967
Okay,
see you later, PP.

06:21.002 --> 06:22.635
[ Giggles ]
Stop calling me that!

06:22.670 --> 06:25.071
Hey, Pan Pan, want to
play this game with us?

06:25.106 --> 06:26.739
Nope,
I'm gonna go to bed --

06:26.774 --> 06:29.175
Got to make sure I get enough
rest before I meet Tom tomorrow.

06:29.210 --> 06:31.544
[ Cellphone rings, vibrates ]
Oh, wait, somebody's calling.

06:31.579 --> 06:32.745
Oh, it's Tom.

06:32.780 --> 06:33.913
<i>Hey, hey, hey!</i>

06:33.948 --> 06:35.648
<i>I'm walking to the bus stop</i>
<i>right now!</i>

06:35.683 --> 06:38.017
That's cool.
I'll walk with you.

06:38.052 --> 06:40.920
<i>[ Video game music playing ]</i>

06:41.622 --> 06:43.556
Oh, I can't wait for
tonight's episode, dude.

06:43.591 --> 06:45.691
I think Kisuk is gonna find out
about the other girl.

06:45.726 --> 06:48.761
<i>No! I want him to stay</i>
<i>in love with Miyoung!</i>

06:48.796 --> 06:50.263
I know! [ Laughs ]

06:50.298 --> 06:51.864
Their friendship is over!

06:51.899 --> 06:52.932
<i>Yeah, that stinks.</i>

06:52.967 --> 06:54.166
Yep.

06:54.201 --> 06:56.269
<i>Hey, Panda,</i>
<i>today was great.</i>

06:56.304 --> 06:58.204
<i>Promise me we'll stay</i>
<i>friends forever.</i>

06:58.239 --> 06:59.672
Pfft, of course, man.

06:59.707 --> 07:02.708
BFFs, remember?
Best friends forever.

07:02.743 --> 07:06.379
[ Sighs ] Stinks we can't be
hanging out right now.

07:06.414 --> 07:07.780
Wish we could be
roommates.

07:07.815 --> 07:09.048
Uh-huh. Yeah.

07:09.083 --> 07:11.384
Cool.
Oh, my bus is here.

07:11.419 --> 07:12.685
I'll talk
to you later, PP.

07:12.720 --> 07:15.021
Okay. See you tomorrow.
[ Giggles ]

07:15.056 --> 07:18.458
Oh, man. Classic Tom.

07:21.929 --> 07:24.563
[ Alarm clock beeps ]

07:24.598 --> 07:26.833
[ Groans ]

07:28.302 --> 07:29.635
[ Beeping stops ]

07:29.670 --> 07:31.504
[ Yawns ]

07:34.508 --> 07:36.743
Aaaah!

07:37.111 --> 07:38.444
Aah! Whoa!

07:38.479 --> 07:41.881
[ Thud ]
What's going on?!

07:41.916 --> 07:43.916
Huh -- Wha?

07:43.951 --> 07:46.419
<i>[ Speaking Korean ]</i>

07:46.454 --> 07:47.920
Good morning!

07:47.955 --> 07:49.288
What is this?

07:49.323 --> 07:50.556
I was gonna surprise you,

07:50.591 --> 07:52.591
but welcome to
our new place, man!

07:52.626 --> 07:55.261
Remember? You said it would be
cool if we were roommates?

07:55.296 --> 07:56.595
So, yep, here it is!

07:56.630 --> 07:58.497
I got everything
you could ask for, man!

07:58.532 --> 08:00.433
Check it out --
- voice activated computer.

08:00.468 --> 08:02.435
[ Computer beeps ]
Nice, right?

08:02.470 --> 08:04.103
And look --
It's a kitchen --

08:04.138 --> 08:06.605
Vegan omelettes at work
as I speak.

08:06.640 --> 08:09.475
And lastly, all of
- "My Sassy Heart" on loop,

08:09.510 --> 08:12.178
and no brothers,
just us BFFs!

08:12.213 --> 08:14.914
So, what do you think?

08:14.949 --> 08:16.782
What do I think?

08:16.817 --> 08:18.250
What do I think?!

08:18.285 --> 08:20.019
Dude, you just
kidnapped me!

08:20.054 --> 08:21.354
What?!
No, no, no, no!

08:21.389 --> 08:23.689
This is too far!
Where the heck are we?!

08:23.724 --> 08:26.292
How did my stuff get here?!
How did I even get here?!

08:26.327 --> 08:27.927
Friendship
brought you here, man.

08:27.962 --> 08:30.629
Love did this --
love and a rental truck.

08:30.664 --> 08:34.033
Friends don't do this
to each other, dingle!

08:34.068 --> 08:35.301
You can't leave.

08:35.336 --> 08:37.103
I'm cooking
vegan omelettes, man.

08:37.138 --> 08:38.704
Don't care!

08:38.739 --> 08:41.040
Voice command,
lock all exits!

08:41.075 --> 08:42.274
[ Locks click ]

08:42.309 --> 08:45.311
[ Door handle jostles ]
Wha...?

08:45.346 --> 08:46.712
Open the door, man.

08:46.747 --> 08:49.015
Not until we finish
our conversation, Panda.

08:49.050 --> 08:53.052
You said you were going to be
best friends forever, remember?

08:53.087 --> 08:55.488
There's no
backing out now.

08:55.523 --> 08:56.856
[ Chuckles nervously ]

08:56.891 --> 08:57.990
Okay, you got it buddy.

08:58.025 --> 09:00.726
Look, I need to go to
the bathroom right now.

09:00.761 --> 09:04.030
Of course.
Bathroom's that way.

09:04.065 --> 09:06.733
[ Sighs ] Good old PP.

09:08.202 --> 09:10.970
Aah!
I got to get out of here!

09:11.005 --> 09:12.071
Huh?

09:12.106 --> 09:14.340
[ Glass shatters ]

09:14.375 --> 09:17.410
Hey, Panda, buddy,
- everything okay in there?

09:17.445 --> 09:19.512
[ Grunts ]

09:19.547 --> 09:21.680
Whoa! Wha! Aah!

09:21.715 --> 09:23.716
There's extra towels
in the right cabinet!

09:23.751 --> 09:25.184
Aah!

09:25.219 --> 09:26.252
Panda!

09:26.287 --> 09:27.420
[ Gasps ]
Stay away, Tom!

09:27.455 --> 09:29.388
Just hang tight, PP!

09:29.423 --> 09:30.723
No, wait! Stop!

09:30.758 --> 09:31.724
Aaaaah!

09:31.759 --> 09:33.426
Oof!

09:33.461 --> 09:35.661
[ Screams ]

09:35.696 --> 09:37.163
What are you
doing here, man?

09:37.198 --> 09:38.764
I'm going back
to my brothers, Tom.

09:38.799 --> 09:40.166
It doesn't matter
if I don't have

09:40.201 --> 09:41.600
everything in common
with them.

09:41.635 --> 09:45.204
But -- - That's not how -
best friends work, Tom!

09:45.239 --> 09:46.439
What have I done?

09:46.474 --> 09:47.740
[ Creaking ]
- Aah!

09:47.775 --> 09:49.409
No!

09:53.080 --> 09:55.281
[ Grunts ]

09:55.316 --> 09:57.216
I'm a horrible
best friend!

09:57.251 --> 09:58.884
Save yourself, Panda!

09:58.919 --> 09:59.919
No! I can pull you up!

09:59.954 --> 10:00.953
No, you can't!

10:00.988 --> 10:03.122
You have very poor
upper-body strength!

10:03.157 --> 10:05.691
It's one of the many things
we have in common!

10:05.726 --> 10:06.459
Tom!

10:06.494 --> 10:08.227
Panda, I'm sorry!

10:08.262 --> 10:09.895
It's okay!
It's gonna be okay!

10:09.930 --> 10:12.098
I-I don't think it is!

10:12.133 --> 10:14.567
Aaah!
- Tom!

10:14.602 --> 10:16.635
Dude, if we don't get
another roommate,

10:16.670 --> 10:17.903
we won't make rent.

10:17.938 --> 10:19.472
We're totally gonna
get evicted.

10:19.507 --> 10:21.407
Isaac doesn't want to lose
his walk-in closet.

10:21.442 --> 10:23.075
-What are we gonna do?
-Aaah!

10:23.110 --> 10:24.076
Oh.

10:24.111 --> 10:25.711
Hey, man, you wouldn't be

10:25.746 --> 10:27.713
looking for a place to live,
would you?

10:27.748 --> 10:29.748
Panda:
Hey, uh, can you guys

10:29.783 --> 10:32.785
call the fire department,
please?

10:34.255 --> 10:36.989
Hot Dog Ninja:<i> Haa!</i>
<i>Feel the wrath of my buns!</i>

10:37.024 --> 10:38.290
Grizz: Yeah!

10:38.325 --> 10:40.593
Man, the animation is so much
better than last season.

10:40.628 --> 10:42.661
Hey, Pan Pan.
Where you been all day?

10:42.696 --> 10:45.097
W-where's your friend,
um, T-Tom, right?

10:45.132 --> 10:46.432
Oh, I, uh --
I don't think

10:46.467 --> 10:48.267
we're gonna be
hanging out anymore.

10:48.302 --> 10:50.169
Oh. I'm sorry, bud.

10:50.204 --> 10:52.004
He seemed, um, nice.

10:52.039 --> 10:53.806
Ice Bear thought
he was a solid five.

10:53.841 --> 10:54.773
[ Slurps ]

10:54.808 --> 10:56.842
Here, come sit with us,
Pan Pan.

10:56.877 --> 10:58.944
Look, you want to watch
that Korean show?

10:58.979 --> 11:00.579
The, uh, uh,
